text: Ðis synd þa landgemere to Alresforda.
Ærest of Cendefer, on ða andheafda.
Andlang andheafda on þa witan dic.
Of beorhlea andlang mearcweges on smalan dene.
Þonon to Bucgan oran, þonon ford be wyrtdene.
Swa be mearce to grenmenes stigele.
Of þam geate to bohmeres stigele.
Of þam geate to Hamerdene geate.
Þonne andlang mearce to Dregtune on þone ford.
Þonon suð andlang mearce to þes gores suð ende.
Andlang Icenan þer Cendefer & Icene cumað togædere.
Andlang Cendefer þer hit ær up eode.
